{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/remove-sharepoint-aspnet-header/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"f676eb6b-aa4b-5469-ac66-5bf5e61cf459","html":"<h1 id=\"remove-sharepoint-aspnet-header\"><a href=\"#remove-sharepoint-aspnet-header\" aria-label=\"remove sharepoint aspnet header permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Remove SharePoint ASP.NET Header</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>보안 상 시스템 정보가 HTTP Header에 노출되는 것을 최소화 하세요. 의 권고로 시작된 작업</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"대상-목록\"><a href=\"#%EB%8C%80%EC%83%81-%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D\" aria-label=\"대상 목록 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>대상 목록</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>X-SharePointHealthScore</li>\n<li>Server</li>\n<li>SPRequestGuid</li>\n<li>X-AspNet-Version</li>\n<li>X-Powered-By</li>\n<li>MicrosoftSharePointTeamServices</li>\n<li>X-MS-InvokeApp</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"x-sharepointhealthscore\"><a href=\"#x-sharepointhealthscore\" aria-label=\"x sharepointhealthscore permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>X-SharePointHealthScore</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>값은 0~10의 숫자</li>\n</ul>\n<p>참고: <a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/jj162162(v=office.12).aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/jj162162(v=office.12).aspx</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The server can monitor the current load and its ability to process requests. If it monitors the load, it can return the load information to the client in a <strong>X-SharePointHealthScore</strong> header. This header specifies a value between 0 and 10, where <strong>0 represents a low load</strong> and a high ability to process requests and <strong>10 represents a high load</strong> and that the server is throttling requests to maintain adequate throughput.  </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>sharepoint 서버의 상태를 0부터 10까지 표현하는 숫자 입니다.<br>이런 숫자마저 보안상 문제가 있다고 한다면, 숨깁니다.</p>\n<p>이 header는 설정으로는 숨길 수가 없고, custom Module을 만들어서 iis 에 등록을 해야 합니다.<br>Init 시점에 PreSendRequestHeaders 에 해당 header를 삭제하는 처리기를 만들어서 추가해 줍니다.<br></p>\n<h2 id=\"server\"><a href=\"#server\" aria-label=\"server permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Server</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>값은 IIS 버전</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"sprequestguid\"><a href=\"#sprequestguid\" aria-label=\"sprequestguid permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SPRequestGuid</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>값은 Guid 문자열</li>\n</ul>\n<p>참고: <a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd908737(v=office.12).aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd908737(v=office.12).aspx</a></p>\n<p>ULS log에서 해당 request guid로 찾기 위해서 기록한다고 합니다.</p>\n<p><strong>X-SharePointHealthScore</strong>, <strong>Server</strong>, <strong>SPRequestGuid</strong> 헤더들은 IIS URL Rewrite module을 설치해서 처리할 수도 있고, 위에서 나온 custom Module을 만들어서 처리할 수도 있습니다.</p>\n<p>IIS URL Rewrite module 통한 header 값 삭제</p>\n<ol>\n<li>서버변수에 RESPONSE_{{HEADER이름}} 추가 (전부 대문자로)</li>\n<li>\n<p>아웃바운드 규칙 추가</p>\n<ol>\n<li>검색 번위: 서버 변수</li>\n<li>변수 이름: 위에 추가한 변수</li>\n<li>변수 값: 패턴과 일치, 사용: 정규식</li>\n<li>패턴: .* (모든거 다)</li>\n<li>작업 유형: 재작성</li>\n<li>값: 빈칸 (기존 서버 변수 값 바꾸기 체크)</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"x-aspnet-version\"><a href=\"#x-aspnet-version\" aria-label=\"x aspnet version permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>X-AspNet-Version</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>값은 ASP.NET Version (2.0.xxx)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>web.config 파일에 system.web > httpRuntime 설정을 찾아서 <code class=\"language-text\">enableVersionHeader=&quot;false&quot;</code> 속성을 추가합니다.<br>하위에 응용 프로그램에서 별도로 true로 설정하지 않으면 상속을 받아서 header 숨김이 처리 됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"xml\"><pre class=\"language-xml\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>configuration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>system.web</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>httpRuntime</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">enableVersionHeader</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>false<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>system.web</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>configuration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 설정하는 script</span>\nappcmd.exe <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> config <span class=\"token string\">\"경로이름\"</span> -section:system.web/httpRuntime /enableVersionHeader:<span class=\"token string\">\"False\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"x-powered-by\"><a href=\"#x-powered-by\" aria-label=\"x powered by permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>X-Powered-By</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>값은 ASP.NET, PHP 등등 기술의 이름 중 하나</li>\n</ul>\n<p>IIS 관리자 > HTTP 응답 헤더에서 삭제 가능</p>\n<p>또는, web.config에서 아래와 같이 처리하면 됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"xml\"><pre class=\"language-xml\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>configuration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>system.webServer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  \t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>httpProtocol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    \t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>customHeaders</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      \t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>remove</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>X-Powered-By<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>customHeaders</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>httpProtocol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>system.webServer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>configuration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"microsoftsharepointteamservices\"><a href=\"#microsoftsharepointteamservices\" aria-label=\"microsoftsharepointteamservices permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>MicrosoftSharePointTeamServices</h2>\n<p>참고: <a href=\"https://wmostafaw.com/2013/08/31/removing-sharepoint-2013-version-form-http-header/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://wmostafaw.com/2013/08/31/removing-sharepoint-2013-version-form-http-header/</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong><em>NOTE: this may effect other applications like InfoPath.</em></strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>SharePoint 버전을 표기하는 header로, 이 header가 없으면 infopath에서 sharepoint 연계된 작업을 할 때 영향을 받습니다.</p>\n<p>숨기는 방법은 <strong>X-Powered-By</strong> 와 동일하게 HTTP 응답 헤더에서 삭제 가능하고, web.config 에서 remove 노드를 추가하는 방법으로도 가능합니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"x-ms-invokeapp\"><a href=\"#x-ms-invokeapp\" aria-label=\"x ms invokeapp permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>X-MS-InvokeApp</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>값은 1; RequireReadOnly 이런 식</li>\n</ul>\n<p>참고: <a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765500(v=office.12).aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dn765500(v=office.12).aspx</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This protocol uses the <strong>X-MS-InvokeApp</strong> response header to signal that the client can pass the document URL directly to a registered client application rather than downloading the document first. This header is defined in ABNF syntax as follows: </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>사실 무슨 기능을 하는 지 정확히는 모르겠지만,, 보안 상 문제가 된다고 하면 header를 삭제합니다.</p>\n<p>숨기는 방법은 <strong>X-Powered-By</strong>, <strong>X-AspNet-Version</strong> 와 동일합니다.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/remove-sharepoint-aspnet-header/","tagSlugs":["/tag/share-point/","/tag/config/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2018-05-09T00:00:00.000Z","description":"보안을 위해 서버 정보가 노출되는 http Header 제거","tags":["SharePoint","Config"],"title":"Remove SharePoint ASP.NET Header","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/remove-sharepoint-aspnet-header/"}}}